result.longName: Jiangsu Hongtu High Technology Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Jiangsu Hongtu High Technology Co., Ltd. primarily engages in retail, electronics manufacturing, Internet finance, and real estate development activities in the People's Republic of China. The company retails computers, telecommunications, smart living, digital products, DIY computer assembly and IT accessories, various products and accessories, various external devices, network and server equipment, office automation and supplies and other accessory products, software products and IT books, service products, etc. It also offers various services and support, including on-site maintenance, system installation and commissioning, application guidance, technical maintenance, after-sale services, etc. In addition, the company researches, develops, produces, and sells various optical communication products, such as fiber optic and power cables, communication cables, power carrier equipment, optical fiber access equipment, distribution automation and smart instrumentation systems, video surveillance systems, communication power supply systems, and program-controlled switching equipment, as well as manufactures communications equipment, optical cable, consumer electronics, computers, and printers. Additionally, the company engages in the processing of copper. Jiangsu Hongtu High Technology Co., Ltd. is based in Nanjing, the People's Republic of China.
